00:10:33.330 --> 00:10:36.330
Hanss sauc to par datu bāzu apkampšanu.

00:10:36.330 --> 00:10:38.330
Tu apkamp savu datu bāzi, Tu negribi to laist vaļā,

00:10:38.330 --> 00:10:40.330
