00:11:04.330 --> 00:11:05.330
Klausītāji: Mums.

00:11:05.330 --> 00:11:06.330
TBL: Vai varat pateikt "neapstrādātus datus"?

00:11:06.330 --> 00:11:07.330
Klausītāji: Neapstrādātus datus!

00:11:07.330 --> 00:11:09.330
